item.title: ZbAGL11
item.description: Gene Details: Gene ID: Gene Symbol: ZbAGL11 Gene Name: Genome: Species: Zanthoxylum bungeanum Functional Description: By measuring the gene expression levels and performing cytological analysis, we found that ZbAGL11, a member of the MADS-Box transcription factor family, is highly expressed at the critical stage of apomixis in ZB.
